Umubare w'abarwaye Coronavirus (COVID-19) wiyongera cyane mu muryango w'ibihugu by'i Burayi no mu Bwongereza kuva ku itariki ya 1 Mutarama kugeza ku ya 15 Werurwe 2020.
Umubare w'abarwaye Coronavirus (COVID-19) ufite ingendo zisa n'izo mu bihugu by'umuryango w'ubumwe bw'u Burayi / European Economic Area no mu Bwongereza, ibyo bikaba byemeza ko nubwo icyorezo cya COVID-19 kiri mu byiciro bitandukanye mu bihugu bitandukanye, kigenda cyongera mu buryo bwihuse mu bihugu byose.
Mu gihe u Butaliyani, ibihugu, ibitaro n'ibigo by'ubuvuzi bukomeye byiboneye ko ari byiza, ni ngombwa ko habaho ukwiyemeza kurushaho kubarwara COVID-19, bakeneye kuvurwa no kwivuza cyane cyane.
Ku itariki ya 31 Ukuboza 2019, mu mujyi wa Wuhan mu ntara ya Hubei mu Bushinwa, havumbuwe abantu benshi barwaye indwara y'uburwayi bw'umugongo.
Tariki ya 9 Mutarama 2020, Ikigo cy'Ubushinwa gishinzwe kugenzura no gukumira indwara cyatangaje ko icyorezo cyatewe n'ubwoko bushya bwa coronavirus, ubu izwi nka coronavirus yo mu bwoko bwa 2 (SARS-CoV-2).
Kuva icyo gihe, indwara yatewe na SARS-CoV-2 yatangiye kwitwa icyorezo cya Coronavirus (COVID-19).
Amakuru dufite kugeza ubu avuga ko abagera kuri 80% by'abarwaye COVID-19 barwara mu buryo bworoheje, ni ukuvuga ubwandu bw'imyenda yo mu mpumuro, haba muri pneumonia cyangwa ntayo, kandi abenshi muri bo bakira.
Hafi 14% by'abanduye COVID-19 bahinduka indwara ikomeye cyane igasaba kujya kwa muganga, naho abandi 6% bahinduka abarwayi igihe bakeneye ubuvuzi bukomeye.
Umubare w'abapfa bavurirwa muri COVID-19 uri hafi kuri 4%.
Ubu bushakashatsi busesengura uko COVID-19 ikwirakwira muri buri gihugu cyo mu muryango w'ubumwe bw'u Burayi (EU) / European Economic Area (EEA) no mu Bwongereza, bugereranya uko ikwirakwira muri Hubei mu Bushinwa.
Nanone duhuza umubare w'abanduye COVID-19 muri EU/EEA no mu Bwongereza n'amakuru yo mu Butaliyani kuva tariki 31 Mutarama kugeza tariki 15 Werurwe 2020.
Ibimenyetso by'indwara ya COVID-19 muri EU/EEA no mu Bwongereza
Nyuma y'aho icyorezo cya COVID-19 cyakwiriye mu Bushinwa, cyakwirakwiriye mu bindi bihugu, kandi ubu mu bindi bice by'isi icyorezo cya COVID-19 kigenda gitera imbere mu buryo buhuje n'uko cyateye mu Bushinwa.
Ku itariki ya 11 Werurwe 2020, umuyobozi mukuru w'Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima (OMS) yatangaje ko COVID-19 ari icyorezo.
Mu kinyamakuru Eurosurveillance cyo ku itariki ya 5 Werurwe 2020, Bwana Spiteri na bagenzi be batangaje ko hari abantu ba mbere bemeza ko banduye COVID-19 mu Burayi, bahuriye ku bipimo OMS ifata kugira ngo igaragaze ko barwaye.
Abanduye batatu ba mbere bavuye mu karere ka UE/EEA bagaragaye mu Bufaransa ku wa 24 Mutarama 2020  Abanduye bose uko ari batatu bagarutse baturutse mu mujyi wa Wuhan mu ntara ya Hubei mu Bushinwa.
Ku itariki ya 15 Werurwe 2020, ubwandu bwa COVID-19 bwabonetse mu bihugu byose 30 by'ubumwe bw'ibihugu by'ubumwe bw'u Burayi/EEA no mu Bwongereza, mu gihe kuva ku itariki ya 31 Ukuboza 2019 kugeza kuri uyu munsi, habayeho ubwandu bwa 39,768 n'urupfu rwa 1,727 muri byo, 17 750 harimo ubwandu bwa 1,441 bwahitanye u Butaliyani gusa.
Gutanga amakuru ku ndwara ya COVID-19
Ikigo cy'u Burayi gishinzwe kurwanya no gukumira indwara (ECDC) gisuzuma buri munsi saa munani ku byerekeye umubare w'abanduye COVID-19 muri buri gihugu ku isi, kibikesha amakuru yemewe nk'iminisiteri y'ubuzima y'ibyo bihugu, inzego z'ubuzima z'ibihugu n'uturere ndetse n'umuryango w'abibumbye wita ku buzima (OMS).
Aya makuru akoreshwa mu gusesengura uko COVID-19 ikwirakwira mu bihugu by'ubumwe bw'u Burayi/EEA no mu Bwongereza no kugereranya n'amakuru yo mu Butaliyani.
Nk'ikimenyetso cy'ubwandu bw'abanduye COVID-19 cyateguwe ku minsi 14 hagendewe ku mibare y'abanduye COVID-19 muri buri gihugu cya EU/EEA no mu Bwongereza kuva ku itariki ya 1 Mutarama kugeza ku ya 15 Werurwe 2020.
Nanone twabagejejeho umubare w'abanduye muri buri gihugu ku isaha ya saa munani z'amanywa ku itariki ya 15 Werurwe 2020, ugereranyije n'iy'u Butaliyani kuva ku itariki ya 31 Mutarama kugeza ku ya 15 Werurwe 2020.
Uko COVID-19 ikwirakwira mu bihugu by'ubumwe bw'u Burayi/EEA no mu Bwongereza
Uko ubwandu bwa COVID-19 bw'ibanze bwagendaga bugabanuka mu gihe cy'iminsi 14 mu bihugu by'ubumwe bw'ibihugu by'ubumwe bw'u Burayi n'u Bwongereza muri rusange, byari bihuye n'uko byari bimeze mu ntara ya Hubei mu Bushinwa (ishusho ya 1).
Umubare w'abarwayi ba COVID-19 muri EU/EEA no mu Bwongereza muri rusange watangiye kwiyongera ahagana ku itariki ya 21 Gashyantare, ku itariki ya 28 Gashyantare 2020 habaye igiterane gikomeye cy'icyo kimenyetso (ibikoresho by'inyongera).
Ibi byatewe ahanini n'umubare w'abanduye uboneka mu Butaliyani wiyongereye cyane, ariko no mu bindi bihugu byose by'umuryango w'ubumwe bw'ibihugu by'ubumwe bw'u Burayi/EEA no mu Bwongereza, habayeho kwiyongera kw'ubwandu bwa COVID-19 (Ibindi bitekerezo).
Mu ishusho ya 2 hagaragaza umubare w'abanduye COVID-19 mu bihugu by'ubumwe bw'ibihugu by'ubumwe bw'u Burayi n'u Bwongereza ugereranyije n'umubare nk'uwo w'u Butaliyani kuva ku itariki ya 31 Mutarama kugeza ku ya 15 Werurwe 2020.
Aya makuru agaragaza ko umubare w'abamaze kwandura ku isaha ya saa munani z'amanywa ku wa 15 Werurwe mu bindi bihugu 15 by'umuryango w'ubumwe bw'ibihugu by'ubumwe bw'u Burayi n'u Bwongereza, ugereranywa n'uw'i Butaliyani mu byumweru bitatu gusa mbere yaho.
Ibyavuye mu bushakashatsi bwacu bigaragaza ko umubare w'abanduye COVID-19 wiyongereye cyane muri EU/EEA no mu Bwongereza.
Uko ubwandu bwa COVID-19 bwiyongera ku bwinshi, bituma umuntu abona ko icyorezo cyugarije ibihugu byose ku muvuduko ugereranywa.
Ibi bikaba bibaho nubwo hari intambwe zitandukanye mu bihugu bitandukanye, hakaba hari uburyo butandukanye bwo gusubiza ibibazo by'ubuzima bw'abaturage mu bihugu bitandukanye, ndetse wenda hakaba hari n'ingingo zitandukanye zo kumenya umuntu cyangwa se uburyo bwo gutoranya abarwayi kugira ngo bagerageze gupima COVID-19, harimo no gupima ku buryo bufatika.
Mu ntangiriro z'ukwezi kwa Werurwe 2020, abaganga bo mu turere twatewe n'iki cyorezo mu Butaliyani bavuze ko abagera kuri 10% by'abarwaye COVID-19 bakeneye ubuvuzi bukomeye, naho itangazamakuru rivuga ko ibitaro n'ibigo by'ubuvuzi bukomeye muri utwo turere byuzuye.
Kugeza ubu amakuru ku barwayi ba COVID-19 bajya mu bitaro no (cyangwa) mu bigo by'ubuvuzi bukomeye muri EU/EEA, aboneka gusa ku kigero cya 6 ku ijana na 1 ku ijana by'abanduye (amakuru ntabwo aboneka).
Ariko kandi, hakenewe gukusanywa amakuru y'uburyo bwose kugira ngo haboneke amakuru y'ubu ariho, agaragaza umubare w'abamaze kwandikwa n'umubare w'abapfuye.
Ubushakashatsi bwakozwe mu 2010-2011 bwagaragaje ko mu Burayi habayeho ukwiyongera gukomeye kw'ibitanda mu bigo by'ubuvuzi bukomeye no mu bigo by'ubuvuzi bukomeye: mu Budage habayeho ibitanda 29,2 ku bantu 100.000, mu Butaliyani habayeho ibitanda 4,2.
Ibi bivuze ko ibindi bihugu bishobora kuba bifite ibikoresho byinshi cyangwa bike ugereranyije n'u Butaliyani (ibitanda 12.5 mu bigo by'ubuvuzi bukomeye no mu bigo by'ubuvuzi bukomeye ku baturage 100.000 mu 20102011).
Raporo ya gatandatu ya ECDC isubirwamo ku byerekeye ingaruka zo gupima ibyago bya COVID-19 igaragaza uko imibare y'ubuzima igenda yuzuza ingano, igaragaza ibipimo by'ibitaro by'abanduye COVID-19 mu bihugu byose bya EU/EEA no mu Bwongereza, igihe ibyago byo kubura ibitanda mu bigo by'ubuvuzi bukomeye birenga 90%.
