Imibereho y'u Butaliyani n'imikorere iriho mu bindi bihugu bigaragaza ko icyorezo cya COVID-19 kiri gutera imbere mu buryo bwihuse mu bihugu by'ubumwe bw'u Burayi/EEA no mu Bwongereza.
Niyo mpamvu ibihugu, ibitaro n'ibigo by'ubuvuzi bukomeye bigomba kuba biteguye icyorezo cya SARS-CoV-2 kiza ku bantu bagendana na cyo, kandi ntikigabanuke mu gihe kirekire, ndetse n'umubare w'abarwayi ba COVID-19 bakeneye ubuvuzi, cyane cyane ubuvuzi bukomeye, nk'uko bigaragara mu turere twatewe n'iki cyorezo mu Butaliyani.
Nkuko bivugwa mu cyegeranyo cya ECDC cy'ibisubizo by'igihembwe cya Raporo y'Icyorezo, uburyo bw'ubuhanga, bw'ubutabazi n'ubushakashatsi bufatika, buva ku budahangarwa bugana ku kugabanya ingaruka, ni ingenzi cyane mu guhashya ikwirakwira rya SARS-COV-2, kuko mu gihe abantu bafata imyanzuro n'ibitaro bizaba biteze kwiyongera mu buryo bwihuse, bishobora kuba bitagira igihe gihagije cyo gutekereza, gufata no gukosora uko byagenda kose mu gihe ibyo bitakozwe hakiri kare.
