Icyorezo cya Coronavirus 2019 (COVID-19), cyatewe na Coronavirus yo mu bwoko bwa 2 (SARS-CoV-2), cyabaye ikibabaje ku bantu: kugeza ubu mu Bushinwa no mu bindi bihugu by'isi hapfuye abantu barenga 3000, naho umubare w'abanduye urenga ibihumbi 80.
Kimwe na SARS-CoV yo mu bwoko bw'umuntu ku giti cye, yateje abantu benshi indwara ikomeye yo guhumeka mu mwaka wa 2003, SARS-CoV-2 ishobora no guhitana intama z'impumyi ikoresheje uburyo busa.
Ariko COVID-19 ifite ubukana buke bw'indwara n'ubwandu buke kurusha SARS, ariko ni icyorezo cyandura cyane kandi cyandura abantu bakuze kurusha abakiri bato, abagabo bakagira ubwandu bwinshi kurusha abagore.
Mu gusubiza ku kwiyongera kwa vuba kw'ibitabo byandika ku ndwara nshya, iyi ngingo itanga isuzuma ry'ibintu byose by'ingenzi byakozwe mu bushakashatsi bw'ingenzi.
Tuzasuzuma ibintu by'ibanze mu bijyanye n'indwara, etiologie, virologie, gusuzuma, kuvura, kumenya uko zizagenda no kwirinda iyi ndwara.
Nubwo hari ibibazo byinshi bitaraba, twizeye ko iki gice kizadufasha kumenya indwara iteje akaga kandi tukayirandura burundu.
Umunsi mukuru w'ihangu (umwaka mushya w'u Bushinwa) wa 2020 waje ku itariki ya 25 Mutarama, wabaye ikintu kitigeze kibaho kandi kitazibagirana ku Bashinwa bose, bahamagariwe kuguma mu rugo mu gihe cyose cy'umunsi mukuru no mu byumweru byinshi nyuma yaho kubera icyorezo cy'indwara nshya.
Kubera ko iyi virusi ifite ibimenyetso byinshi by'indwara ya Coronavirus (CoV) yatumye indwara y'ubuhumekero bukomeye (SARS) iba mu mwaka wa 2003, ku itariki ya 11 Gashyantare 2020 Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima (OMS) ryayise SARS-CoV-2, naho indwara ifitanye isano nayo yitwa coronavirus infection 19 (COVID-19).
Iki cyorezo cyatangiye mu mujyi wa Wuhan mu Bushinwa, gikwira igihugu cyose vuba, nyuma kiza gukwira mu bindi bihugu hafi 50.
Ku itariki ya 2 Werurwe 2020, abantu barenga 80,000 banduye COVID-19, abasaga 40.000 barakize, abasaga 3.000 barapfuye.
OMS iragabisha ko COVID-19 ari umwanzi w'ibanze w'abaturage kandi ko ishobora guteza akaga kurusha iterabwoba.
PubMed (https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/) ivuga ko mu gihe kitageze ku mezi abiri hasohotse ibitabo birenga 200 kuri COVID-19, birimo ingingo zivuga ku ndwara y'ibicurane, icyorezo, inyigo, indwara n'uburyo bwo kuvurwa, guhera ku nkuru ya mbere yo ku itariki ya 7 Mutarama 2020, yagaragaje ko virusi yavuye ku barwayi benshi.
Iyi nkuru ni igamije gusobanura neza ibyo ubushakashatsi bwakozwe mu bijyanye n'ubushakashatsi bushya kandi bukomeje gutera imbere.
Tuzagerageza kugereranya COVID-19 na SARS n'indi ndwara ya coronavirus (MERS) y'ubuhumekero bwo mu Burasirazuba bwo Hagati, yatangiye mu 2012.
Nanone tuzasuzuma ibintu bizwi ku birebana no kwirinda no kumenya uko indwara zizagenda, hamwe n'ibindi bibazo by'ingenzi.
Koronavirusi zakunze kuba mu ndwara zitera indwara zitera indwara z'ubwonko zitera urupfu ku bantu, zikaba ziterwa n'ibipimo bigera kuri 15 ku ijana by'indwara z'ubuhumekero rusange 4.
Nyamara muri iki kinyejana, twahuye na coronavirus z'abantu ziteye indwara nyinshi inshuro ebyiri, ari zo coronavirus yo mu bwoko bwa SARS-CoV-2 na coronavirus yo mu bwoko bwa MERS-CoV, zatumye indwara zandura, mu Bushinwa mu 2003 no muri Arabiya Sawudite mu 2012, kandi vuba aha zikaza kugera mu bindi bihugu byinshi, aho indwara n'urupfu byagiye byiyongera cyane.
Bityo, COVID-19 iriho ubu ni icyorezo cya gatatu cya coronavirus mu mateka y'abantu.
Nk'uko bigaragara ku ishusho 1.1, amakuru ku byiciro by'abanduye indwara ya Pneumonia itaramenyekana yatangiriye muri Komisiyo y'Igihugu y'Ubuzima ya UPRK yo mu mujyi wa Wuhan ku wa 31 Ukuboza 2019.
Nyuma y'iminsi irindwi, hashyizweho urutonde rw'ibinyabuzima bya virusi.
Tariki ya 15 Mutarama 2020 nibwo habaye ubwicanyi bwa mbere mu mujyi wa Wuhan.
Hagati aho, icyorezo cyakwirakwiriye mu migi, mu ntara no mu bihugu by'abaturanyi.
Tariki 20 Mutarama nibwo abaganga bamenyekanye ko banduye, bituma umuntu ashobora kwandura virusi.
Tariki ya 23 Mutarama, mu mujyi wa Wuhan hashyizweho icyorezo, imodoka rusange zo mu mujyi zirangira gukora.
Ku itariki ya 24 Mutarama, ubushakashatsi bwa mbere bwakozwe kuri iyi ndwara bwagaragaje ko mu bantu 41 banduye Coronavirus, 21 bafitanye isano ya bugufi n'isoko ry'ibikomoka ku nyanja ryo mu mujyi wa Wuhan, aho abantu babona ko ari ho hatangirira ubwandu buturutse ku nyamaswa itaramenyekana.
Ku itariki ya 30 Mutarama, OMS yatangaje ko icyorezo cya Coronavirus ari ihungabana rikomeye ku isi mu rwego rw'ubuzima bw'abaturage.
Igihe iyi raporo yatangiraga kwandikwa , icyo cyorezo cyari cyaramaze gukwira mu Bushinwa bwose , kikaba cyaramaze kugera mu bindi bihugu bigera kuri 50 byo ku isi (ishusho y'ibisobanuro ku ishusho ya 2.2).
Kubera ko ibintu byihuta, icyorezo cyaba gikomeye cyane n'ubundi gishobora kuba gikomeye cyane, biracyari ngombwa ko hagira umuntu umenya.
Ku itariki ya 11 Gashyantare 2020, hakurikijwe ubushakashatsi bwakozwe n'abaganga benshi, bitabiriye abagera ku 8,866, barimo abagera ku 4,021 banduye COVID-19, hashyizweho ishusho y'icyorezo (https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/UlBi-HX_rHPXa1qHA2bhdA).
Abantu bose bafite imyaka yose barwaye SARS-CoV-2, ariko abenshi muri bo bari hagati y'imyaka 30 na 65.
Hafi kimwe cya kabiri (47.7%) cy'abanduye bari hejuru y'imyaka 50, bake cyane bari munsi y'imyaka 20, kandi 14 gusa ni bo bari munsi y'imyaka 10.
Urubyiruko rw'abagabo rurandura SARS-CoV-2 kurusha abagore (0,27/100 000).
COVID-19 yari ikwirakwiriye mu matsinda cyane cyane mu ntara ya Hubei no mu turere duturanye.
Ku kigereranyo kuva igihe ibimenyetso bya COVID-19 byatangiriye kugeza igihe umuntu yabonetseho indwara, hashize iminsi 5 (29).
Igihe cyo gupima cyibasiye ku buryo bw'ibanze iminsi 4,8 (3,07,2).
Kuva ibimenyetso byatangira kugaragara kugeza igihe umuntu yapfiriye, hashize iminsi 9,5 (4,813) ku kigereranyo.
Igishoro cy'ibanze cyo kubyara (R0) cyakozwe ku kigero cya 3,77 (95 % CI: 3,514,05), naho R0 ikosowe yagaragaye ku kigero cya 2,234,82.
Ku itariki ya 23 Mutarama 2020, umubare w'abanduye wariyongereye cyane, ugereranyije n'ibihe by'imodoka nyinshi z'ingendo mu gihe cyo kwizihiza umwaka mushya w'u Bushinwa.
Urupfu mu barwayi bafite indwara yemejwe rwari 1,44% (95% CI: 1,101,86%) naho igipimo cy'uburwayi cy'abarwayi cyakorerwagaho guhuza n'uburwayi ni 3,06% (95% CI: 2,024,59%).
Ibintu bitatu by'ingenzi byateje akaga mu gihe umuntu arwaye COVID-19 ni: igitsina (cy'umugabo), imyaka (≥60) n'ibyago bikomeye byo kurwara indwara ya pneumonie.
Koronavirusi ni virusi nini cyane z'uruhu, zifite umurongo umwe w'inkingi ya RNA.
Zigaburwa mu bwoko bune ari bwo alfa, beta, gamma na delta, kandi abantu bazi ko ari zo za coronavirusi za alfa na beta.
Iyo umuntu arwaye virusi ya SARS na MERS, glikoprotiyini y'ibinyampeke (S) ifatana n'ibikoresho by'ingirabuzimafatizo by'ingingo za angiotensin-transforming enzyme yo mu bwoko bwa 2 (ACE2) na dipeptidylpeptidaze-4 (DPP4) hakurikijwe ibyo, hanyuma igakora imiterere y'ingirabuzimafatizo.
Mu cyitoplasma, genome ya RNA y'umugera ihita isohoka; iyo genome ya RNA imaze gusubirana na glikoproteine z'uruhu n'imiterere ya proteine ya nucleocapside, iba irimo virion, hanyuma igashyiramo virusi.
Raporo ya mbere ku bijyanye n'uruhererekane rwa genome ya SARS-CoV-2 yasohotse ku itariki ya 10 Mutarama 2020.
Bemejwe ko SARS-CoV-2 ari ubwoko bushya bwa betacoronavirus, genome yayo ihuriyeho na 99,98% ku bipimo 10 bikurikirana byavanywe mu gace ka mbere k'icyorezo, ku isoko ry'ibikomoka ku mazi rya Huanan mu mujyi wa Wuhan.
Mu mico ya SARS-CoV-2 ni hafi ya SARS-CoV kurusha iya MERS-CoV.
Hakoreshejwe ikoranabuhanga ry'ubushakashatsi, ibice bya SARS-CoV-2 byabonetse mu bice by'ubuhumekero bw'umuntu.
Bemeza ko ingirabuzima fatizo ya ACE2 ari yo ikira SARS-CoV-2, kimwe na SARS-CoV.
Ariko kandi, poroteyine ya S ya SARS-CoV-2 ifitanye isano n'ikinga ACE2 ry'umuntu ku buryo idakomeye kurusha SARS-CoV, ibyo bikaba bisobanura ko SARS-CoV-2 ituma abarwayi barwara indwara ifite uburemere buke kurusha SARS-CoV.
SARS-CoV-2 ishobora no gukora poroteyine y'ubuzima bugufi itari izwi mbere, ihimbwe orf3b, n'indi ihimbwe orf8.
Poroteyine ya SARS-CoV-2 orf3b ishobora kugira uruhare mu gutuma virusi iba igendana n'indwara kandi igahagarika IFNβ; ariko orf8 nta domaine cyangwa impamvu y'imikorere izwiho.
Tariki 18 Gashyantare 2020, itsinda ry'abanditsi riyobowe na Zhou ryatanze raporo ku isanzure rya tomografiya ya cryoelectronic ya enzyme ACE2 y'abantu ifite icyemezo cya 2,9 Å mu murenge hamwe na B0AT1 isakurwaho amasiniki.
Basanze iyi kompanyi irimo imiterere y'ibishushanyo byahise n'ibishushanyo byahise, ikora nk'umuti w'ibishushanyo bya ACE2-B0AT1, kandi ishobora guhuza poroteyine ebyiri za S, bikaba ari ikimenyetso cy'uko umuntu ashobora kumenya ko afite coronavirus cyangwa ko afite virusi.
B0AT1 ishobora kuba intego y'ubuvuzi mu gihe ukoresha imiti yo gupima indwara ya SARS-CoV-2.
