Imico n'ubwoko bwa SARS-CoV-2 kugeza ubu biracyari bitaramenyekana.
Mu byiciro by'ubushakashatsi SARS-CoV na MERS-CoV zishobora kubaho amasaha 48 mu gihe cy'ubushyuhe bw'ikirere n'iminsi 5 mu gihe cy'ubushyuhe buri munsi ya 20 °C no mu gihe cy'umwanda wa 4050%.
SARS-CoV-2 ishobora kugira ibintu nk'ibyo.
Birazwi ko SARS-CoV-2 ifite ubukana bw'umuco wa farasi (UV) n'ubushyuhe bugera kuri 56 °C mu gihe cy'iminota 30; ishobora kubuza virusi gukora neza, harimo ether, 75% ethyl alcohol, chlorine, peroxyde, chlorophoreside n'ibindi byuma bivamo ibinure ariko bidakora chlorhexydine.
