Ubusanzwe, iyo virusi yinjiye mu mubiri w'umuntu, ubusanzwe iba imenya uburyo bw'umubiri w'umuntu uvuka binyuze mu buryo bw'ibimenyetso (ORR), harimo ibikorerwa mu bwoko bwa C, ibikorerwa mu bwoko bwa Toll, ibikorerwa mu bwoko bwa NOD n'ibikorerwa mu bwoko bwa RIG-I.
Binyuze mu buryo butandukanye, virusi itera kugaragaza ibimenyetso by'ubushongi, gukura kw'ingirabuzimafatizo za dendrites no kuvugurura interférone y'icyiciro cya I, bigabanya ikwirakwira ry'iyi virusi kandi bigateza imbere fagocytosis ya macrophages ku birebana na virusi ya virusi.
Ariko kubera ko SARS-CoV ifite uruvange rwa N, ishobora kwirinda kugira ingaruka z'ubwirinzi.
Nyuma y'igihe gito, kurwanya virusi byinjizwa mu buryo bw'umubiri.
Imyuka yitwa T lymphocytes, harimo n'ingirabuzima fatizo za CD4+ na CD8+, igira uruhare rukomeye mu kurinda umubiri.
CD4+ zituma virusi ikora za antibodies mu ngirabuzimafatizo za B, naho CD8+ zituma virusi ikora neza.
T-helper zifasha mu kuvura imyuka irwanya ubwandu, ikagira uruhare mu kurinda ingirabuzimafatizo.
Ariko kandi, coronavirus ishobora guhungabanya imikorere y'ingirabuzimafatizo za T, igatuma zipfa.
