Urugero, imiti yavuye ku murwayi wari warakize yagabanyije virusi ya MERS-CoV.
Ku rundi ruhande, iyo umubiri w'umubiri urenze ubushobozi bwawo bwo kwamagana indwara, usanga hari ingufu nyinshi z'umwimerere zituma habaho ingufu nyinshi z'umwimerere, zikabangamira cyane ibihaha n'ibindi bice by'umubiri, ndetse zikaba zishobora no gutuma umuntu apfa.
Icyorezo cya SARS-CoV-2, kigaragara mu buryo bw'umwihariko mu bantu benshi, gishobora gutera abantu bakuze bafite indwara ziterwa n'iyo ndwara ndetse n'abagore batwite.
Abantu bafite virusi nyinshi cyangwa bafite ibibazo by'ubwirinzi ni bo bafite amahirwe menshi yo kwandura.
Dukurikije ibyavuye mu bushakashatsi bwakozwe ku bantu 425 ba mbere banduye mu mujyi wa Wuhan, igihe cy'ubwirinzi rusange cya SARS-CoV-2 kigera ku minsi 1 kugeza kuri 14, ahanini ni iminsi 37.
Ariko ubushakashatsi bwakozwe ku bantu 1099 bwagaragaje ko igihe cyo kuryamana cyamaze iminsi 3 ku kigereranyo, kandi ko icyo gihe cy'iminsi 0 kugeza kuri 24.
Nyuma y'aho, ubushakashatsi bwagaragajwe haruguru bushingiye ku bantu 8.866, bwagaragaje ko igihe cyo gupima cy'iminsi 4.8 (3.07.2).
Ni ngombwa ko inzego z'ubuzima zikosora igihe cyo gushyiraho ingamba zo kwirinda abantu, zigakoresha ingamba zigaragaza igihe umuntu amara mu gihe cyo kurwara, bityo bikagufasha kwirinda ko uwo mugera ukwirakwira ku bantu barwaye indwara idafite ibimenyetso.
Mu gihe cy'iminsi 14 abantu bagendana na virusi cyangwa banduye iyi virusi, ni bwo bakunze kujya mu kato.
