Icyorezo cya COVID-19 akenshi kigaragazwa n'ubushyuhe bwinshi, kandi bishobora kuba ari bwo bwonyine cyangwa se bigaragazwa n'ibindi bimenyetso, urugero nko gusama, guhumeka nabi, kubabara mu ngingo, guhinda umushyitsi, umutwe, kuribwa mu ijosi, kwicurika, kubabara mu gituza, isesemi, kurira no kuvira.
Hari abarwayi bamaze icyumweru barwaye, bagaragaje ko bahumeka neza kandi (cyangwa) ko bafite ikibazo cy'ihindagurika ry'umuvuduko w'amaraso.
Mu gihe cy'imimerere ikomeye, indwara yateye imbere mu buryo bwihuse, maze abarwayi barwara indwara y'ubuhumekero, icyago cya septic, acidosis metabolique na coagulopatie.
Abarwayi bafite ubushyuhe bwinshi (burenze urugero) n'ibimenyetso by'indwara zo mu myanya y'ubuhumekero (symptoms) n'umuriro ukaze bagombye gushakishwa virusi mu rwego rwo gusuzuma hakiri kare, ndetse n'iyo nta ngorane zibaho mu mashusho y'igiceri.
Ubushakashatsi bwakozwe mu mpera z'Ukuboza 2019, bwagaragaje ibimenyetso bikurikira: 98%  ubushyuhe bwinshi, 76%  ububabare bw'ubushyuhe, 55%  guhumeka n' 3%  isahane; 8% by'abarwayi basabwaga guhumeka ibihaha.
Ibi byakozwe mu bushakashatsi bubiri bwa vuba aha ku bantu banduye mu muryango no ku bantu batagira ibimenyetso.
Ibisubizo bihuye byabonetse mu mwaka wa 2012 mu bushakashatsi bwakozwe ku barwayi bafite MERS-CoV, bafite ibimenyetso bikuru kandi byari ubushyuhe bwinshi (98%) , ubuhumekero bwumye (47%) no guhumeka (55%).
Ariko 80% by'aba bantu basabwaga guhumeka ibihaha, ibi bikaba biruta kure cyane abarwayi ba COVID-19, kandi bihuye n'umubare munini w'abapfa bahitanwa na MERS kurusha abahitanywe na COVID-19.
Abarwayi bafite indwara ya MERS na bo bagaragaje ko bafite ikibazo cy ' uruhu (26%), n 'ububabare bw ' mu ijosi (21%).
Ibimenyetso by'ingenzi by'abarwayi ba SARS ni ubushyuhe (99100 %), ubuhumekero bwumye (2975 %), guhumeka (4042 %), indwara yo mu nda (2025 %) n'ububabare bw'umugongo (1325 %), naho guhumeka mu mahaha bisaba 1420 % by'abarwayi.
Ku itariki ya 14 Gashyantare, abantu bapfa bazize COVID-19 bari 2%, naho umubare w'abamaze kwandura ku isi wose ugera kuri 66,576.
Mu gihe bagereranyije n'iyi mibare, urupfu rwa SARS rwari 10 ku ijana by'abantu 8.096 banduye muri Ugushyingo 2002.
Mu gihe cya MERS ubushakashatsi bwakozwe muri Kamena 2012 bwagaragaje ko abantu bapfa ku kigero cya 37% mu bantu 2,494 bavurwa.
Ubushakashatsi bwa mbere bwagaragaje ko igipimo cy'ibanze cy'ubwoko bwa SARS-CoV-2 (R0) cyashyizwe ku rwego rwa 6,47 ku kigero cya 95% cy'ubuziranenge (CI) kiri hagati ya 5,717,23, mu gihe R0 ya SARS-CoV yari hagati ya 2 na 4.
Gereranya SARS-CoV-2 na MERS-CoV na SARA-CoV ku bimenyetso, urupfu n'igitigiri cya R0 biri mu Gifatizo 1.1.
Ibipimo byatanzwe hejuru bigaragaza ko SARS-CoV-2 ifite ubushobozi bwo gukwirakwira kurusha MERS-CoV na SARS-CoV, ariko igipimo cy'ubwandu bw'iyi virusi nshya kiri hasi ugereranyije n'izo ebyiri za nyuma.
Ku bw'ibyo, guhangana n'icyorezo cya SARS-CoV-2 bizoroha cyane kurusha icyorezo cya MERS-CoV na SARS-CoV.
Ubusanzwe, iyo umuntu yanduye mu muryango umwe cyangwa mu itsinda ry'abantu bahuriye hamwe ku mpamvu runaka cyangwa bari kumwe mu modoka runaka, urugero nk'inyanja y'inyanja.
Abarwayi bakundaga kujya mu mujyi wa Wuhan cyangwa mu tundi turere twatewe n'iki cyorezo, bakabana na ho cyangwa bagasangira n'abanduye cyangwa abarwayi mu byumweru bibiri bishize mbere y'uko indwara itangira.
Ariko amakuru atangwa n'inkuru avuga ko abantu bashobora kuba ari abafite virusi nta bimenyetso byayo mu gihe kirenga ibyumweru bibiri, kandi ko abarwayi bavuye mu bitaro bashobora kongera kuba abafite virusi, bikaba ari ikimenyetso cy'akaga ko kongera igihe cyo kuba mu kato.
Mu gihe cy'imyanya ndangagitsina, mu maraso y'abagabo, iyo maraso ari menshi cyangwa ari make, haba mu maraso y'abagabo cyangwa se mu mubiri.
Urugero, mu barwayi 1099 barwaye COVID-19 basanze bafite ibipimo bya lymphocytes < 4×109/L, harimo n'ibipimo bya leukocyte < 1×109/L, ndetse n'ibipimo bya asparagine-aminotransferase na virusemia.
Mu maraso y'abarwayi bamwe basanze bafite ingano nyinshi z'ingingo z'umubiri, ingano z'umubiri n'iz'ibinyabuzima by'ibinyabuzima, mu gihe abenshi basanze bafite ingano nyinshi z'ingingo z'umubiri z'ibinyabuzima by'ibinyabuzima by'ibinyabuzima (C-reactive protein) n'iz'ibinyabuzima by'ibinyabuzima (erythrocytes) mu maraso.
Mu barwayi barwaye indwara y'indwara y'ibicurane, ibipimo bya D dimer, ikoreshwa mu gutsemba imiterere y'amaraso, byarazamutse, naho umubare w'imiterere y'amaraso ugakomeza kugabanuka.
Mu barwayi benshi bafite COVID-19 mu gihe bagenzuraga igitsina cyabo mu mashusho ya radiografi, basanze bafite indwara z'ibicurane, zigaragazwa n'umwijima utari umwe ku mpande zombi cyangwa umwijima w'ibirahuri by'ibirahuri mu bihaha.
Abarwayi bakunze kugira indwara y'ubuhumekero idasanzwe, indwara y'ibihaha ikabije n'indwara y'ubuhumekero ikabije (ORP).
Iyo ubwonko bw'ibinyabuzima bwiyongera, ubwirakabiri butarimo gutegekwa, ubwiyongere bw'amazi n'ubwonko buteye imbere bituma ubushyuhe bw'umwuka buhinduka cyane.
Imikorere mibi y'ibihaha by'ibihaha by'ubwoko bwa I na II igabanya igipimo cy'ibihaha bikora ku butaka kandi igatuma ubwirakabiri bw'ibihaha bugabanuka, bityo bigatuma ibihaha bidashobora kwikuba kandi bigatuma birushaho kugwa.
Ibyo bituma abantu benshi bahura n'ibigeragezo bikomeye cyane.
Tariki 18 Gashyantare 2020, isuzuma rya mbere ry'ubuvuzi bwa COVID-19 ryagaragaje ko impyiko z'ibihaha zagiye zisanzura, imyenda ya hyaline n'ihindagurika ry'imyanya ndangagitsina y'amaraso, naho ingirabuzimafatizo za syncytial nyinshi mu barwayi b'ibihaha bapfuye bazize iyo ndwara, zihuye n'uburwayi bwa virusi n'uburwayi bwa ODR kandi zisa n'ibyabonetse mu barwayi ba SARS na MERS.
Mu gusuzuma COVID-19 hakoreshejwe uburyo bwo gutahura RNA ya SARS-CoV-2 binyuze mu kuvugurura imiterere ya polymease na transcriptase (PCR na transcriptase).
Ariko kandi, kubera ko hari ibimenyetso byinshi by'ibinyoma byahungabanya ubuzima bw'abantu, bishobora gutuma icyorezo gitera imbere vuba, kuva ku itariki ya 13 Gashyantare 2020, mu Bushinwa batangiye gushingira ku bipimo bishingiye ku bipimo bya muganga (ntibasubire kwifashisha PCR gusa ifite transcriptase y'ibanze).
Uko ni ko byagenze no ku bantu basanze bafite SARS.
