Abashinzwe ubuzima mu Bushinwa bashobora kuvanaho isomo rikomeye kandi bakagira icyo bageraho mu gihe kizaza.
Urugero, inzego z'ubuzima zikwiye: (1) gukora ibitatangazo by'ubwirinzi kurushaho, kuko ijambo ryose ry'ubutumwa buhabwa abaturage kandi rishobora kugira ingaruka ku myifatire n'imyanzuro yabo; (2) gukurikirana no guhangana n'amakuru adasanzwe ava mu mavuriro aho gutegereza raporo z'ibanze ziva ku baganga n'abayobozi; (3) gufata ingamba zikomeye kurushaho zo gukumira icyorezo cy'ubwandu bushobora kuba mu bihe byambere by'iterambere ryacyo, aho guhumuriza abaturage; no (4) gukora imyitozo igamije kandi igira ingaruka nziza kenshi kugira ngo abaturage bamenye neza indwara z'icyorezo kandi bagenzure kandi batere imbere gahunda zo guhangana n'ibyago.
Icyorezo cya COVID-19, cyatewe n'icyorezo cy'indwara y'ubuhumekero bw'icyorezo cy'indwara ikomeye y'indwara y'ubuhumekero y'icyiciro cya kabiri (SARS-CoV-2), kitigeze kibaho, cyatangiye mu mpera z'ukwezi kwa cumi na kabiri 2019.
Mu gihe kitageze ku mezi abiri, iki cyorezo cyageze mu Bushinwa bwose, kandi kugeza ubwo iyi nyandiko yandikwaga, cyakwirakwiriye mu bihugu 50 byo ku isi.
Kubera ko virusi isa cyane na coronavirus yo mu bwoko bwa SARS-CoV kandi ibimenyetso bya COVID-19 bikaba bimeze nk'ibimenyetso bya SARS, COVID-19 yahindutse SARS.
Ariko kandi, hagati ya COVID-19 na SARS hari itandukaniro rikomeye, rikomeye mu bijyanye no gukumira icyorezo no kuvura abarwayi.
COVID-19 ifata abantu bakuze kurusha urubyiruko, n'abagabo kurusha abagore; umubare w'abarwayi bakomeye n'abapfa mu bageze mu za bukuru na bo ni hejuru cyane ugereranyije n'urubyiruko.
Urupfu rwatewe na SARS ni rwo ruruta urw'abafite COVID-19 (10,91%, ugereranyije na 1,44%).
