Ni iki cyatumye SARS-CoV-2 ibaho?
Nubwo hamaze kuvumburwa ko SARS-CoV-2 ifite ibice 96 ku ijana by'indwara ya coronavirus y'ibishwi bibiri bimeze nka SARS, ntitubasha kuvuga ko SARS-CoV-2 yanduye ibishwi.
Ni ikihe gikoko cyabaye ubwoko bw'ikiremwamuntu cyanduye virusi kuva ku nyirayo, urugero nk'impigi, kikajya ku muntu?
Iyo tutazi ibisubizo by'ibibazo bibiri bya mbere, ntidushobora guhagarika icyorezo mu buryo bwuzuye, kandi icyorezo gishobora kwiyongera igihe icyo ari cyo cyose.
Gushushanya ku rwego rwa molekile no gupima ibijyanye n'ubushakashatsi mu binyabuzima byerekanye ko SARS-CoV-2 ifitanye isano na ACE2, ariko se ni gute koko virusi yinjira mu ngirabuzimafatizo z'inzira zo guhumeka ikazana impinduka zikurikiraho?
Ese virusi ifitanye isano n'ingirabuzimafatizo z'ibindi bice by'umubiri zitunganya ACE2?
Iyo tutabonye ibisubizo byumvikana kuri ibyo bibazo, ntidushobora kubona ubuvuzi bwihuse kandi bufite ireme, kandi ntidushobora kubona imiti myiza.
Icyorezo kizakomeza kubaho igihe kingana iki?
Ni gute virusi yihindura mu mibereho yayo mu gihe umuntu anyura ku wundi?
Ese izatera icyorezo ku isi hose, izashira nka SARS cyangwa izongera kugaragara nk'icyorezo cy'ibicurane?
Ibyo bintu ni iby'ingenzi cyane, ariko gusubiza ibyo bibazo n'ibindi byinshi bizadusaba igihe.
Ariko nta kundi twabigenza uretse guhagarika iki cyorezo vuba uko bishoboka kose, tukongera kubaho neza.
Impamvu za virusi ya Coronavirusi
Guhinduka no guhinduka byateye imbere iterambere rya coronavirus (CoV) n'abazayifata, harimo n'abantu, mu gihe cy'imyaka ibarirwa mu bihumbi.
Kugeza mu 2003, byari bizwi ko virusi ebyiri za coronavirusi (HCoV) zitera indwara yoroheje, urugero nk'icyorezo cy'indwara y'imbeho.
Ibimenyetso by'indwara y'ubuhumekero bukomeye (SARS) n'indwara y'ubuhumekero yo mu Burasirazuba bwo Hagati (MERS) byahinduye uko tubona ko koronavirus ishobora guteza akaga n'akaga.
Icyorezo cya Coronavirus cy'indwara yo guhumeka ikomeye y'icyiciro cya kabiri (SARS-CoV-2) cyabaye mu Bushinwa bwo hagati mu mpera z'umwaka wa 2019 cyongeye guhangayikisha abantu ku byerekeye coronavirus, kandi kidutangaza cyane kubera ko iyi virusi ishobora kwandura cyane ariko ikaba ifite ubwandu buke ugereranyije na SARS-CoV.
Icyorezo cya Coronavirus mu bantu ni indwara yo mu bwoko bwa zoonoz, kandi gusobanukirwa aho iyo ndwara ya zoonoz yakomotse bizadufasha cyane.
Icyorezo cya Coronavirus cy'abantu benshi kiva ku nguge, kandi ntizifite ubwandu.
Nanone kandi, hari amabati y'ibinyabuzima bya virusi ya coronavirusi y'abantu azwi cyane.
Gushyiraho inyamaswa zitwara indwara bigira ingaruka ku kwirinda indwara z'abantu.
Kwiga ku mishyikirano y'inyamaswa zitwara coronavirus na byo bishobora gutuma abantu babona ko coronavirus ari icyorezo.
Muri iyi nkuru, dusubiramo amakuru y'abantu barindwi banduye coronavirus, twibanda cyane ku mateka y'ubushakashatsi bwabo, aho bakomoka n'uburyo bwo guhitana hagati y'amoko.
Icy'ingenzi ni uko tugereranya virusi zitandukanye za coronavirusi mu buryo bw'ubwihindurize bw'indwara n'ubushakashatsi bwakozwe ku binyabuzima.
Muri iyo nkuru, hagendewe no ku ndwara y'iki gihe yatewe na coronavirus yabonetse mu mwaka wa 2019 (COVID-19).
Ikindi kandi, ni uko hari ibintu by'ingenzi bikenewe kugira ngo umuntu ahindure abafite virusi, n'ingaruka iterambere ry'iyo virusi rigira ku buremere bw'indwara.
Koronavirusi ni zimwe mu ndwara z'ubwoko bwa Coronaviridae, ari zo virusi z'uruhu zifite umurongo umwe w'intoki z'ubwoko bwa RNA.
Izo virusi zifite genom nini cyane kurusha izindi zose zifite ADN, zifite hagati ya 26 na 32 000 wa nukleotide, zitwa izo virusi kubera uko zimeze, zigereranywa n'ikamba iyo zisuzumwa muri mikorosike.
Mu buryo bw'ikoranabuhanga, virusi ya coronavirusi irimo genom zidakemutse zifite gahunda imwe.
