Hari ibimenyetso bya gijeniyeti bigaragaza ko imbeba n'ibikeri ari byo bikomoka kuri virusi nyinshi za alpha na beta, mu gihe inyoni ari zo zikomoka muri virusi za gamma na delta.
Mu gihe cy'imyaka ibarirwa mu bihumbi, virusi ya corona yagiye ihangana n'ubwoko butandukanye, kandi zimwe muri zo zaragiye zinyura mu bintu bishobora guteza akaga ku bantu.
Kugeza ubu, abantu bamaze kumenya ko hari koronavirusi ndwi.
Muri izo virusi harimo HCoV-229E na HCoV-NL63 zo mu bwoko bwa alphacoronavirus.
Izindi virusi eshanu za betacoronavirus zirimo HCoV-OC43, HCoV-HKU1, coronavirus yo mu bwoko bw'ubuhumekero bukomeye (SARS-CoV), coronavirus yo mu bwoko bw'ubuhumekero bukomeye bwo mu burasirazuba bwo hagati (MERS-CoV) na coronavirus yo mu bwoko bw'ubuhumekero bukomeye bwo mu bwoko bwa kabiri bwa SARS-CoV-2.
Koronavirusi z'abantu HCoV-229E, HCoV-OC43, HCoV-HKU1 na HCoV-NL63 ubusanzwe zitera ibimenyetso by'ubwoko bworoheje, urugero nk'icyorezo cy'indwara y'imbeho n' (cyangwa) icyorezo cy'ibibyimba.
Ibinyuranye n'ibyo, virusi ya SARS-CoV, MERS-CoV na SARS-CoV-2 iherutse kuvumburwa ni indwara ikomeye cyane, zitera indwara z'uburwayi z'inzira zo mu myanya y'ubuhumekero yo hasi mu barwayi benshi cyane bafite ibyago byinshi byo kurwara indwara yo mu myanya y'ubuhumekero (ORD) no kugaragaza ibimenyetso bitari mu myanya y'ubuhumekero.
Umugongo wa mbere wa virusi ya coronavirusi ya HCoV-229E, B814, wavanywe mu cyuma cy'abarwayi barwaye icyorezo cy'ibicurane mu myaka ya 1960.
Kuva icyo gihe, ubushakashatsi bwakozwe ku buryo bunonosoye bwagaragaje byinshi ku virusi za HCoV-229E na HCoV-OC43, zitera ibimenyetso by'ubwandu bw'aho umuntu ari.
Mu by'ukuri, mbere y'uko indwara yo guhumeka ikaze (SARS) itangira, hari igitekerezo cyemerwagaho ko umuntu atagira icyo akora iyo afashwe na koronavirusi.
Icyorezo cya SARS cyo mu mwaka wa 2003 cyari kimwe mu byorezo byateje akaga cyane mu mateka y'iki gihe; abantu barenga 8000 barwaye, naho umubare w'abapfa bose wari ugera kuri 10%.
Nyuma y'imyaka icumi, icyorezo cy'indwara yo guhumeka yo mu Burasirazuba bwo Hagati (MERS) cyateye icyorezo cyamaze igihe kirekire mu karere ka Arabiya, kandi cyakwirakwiriye mu bindi bihugu.
Ikirombe gishya cya Coronavirus (2019-nCoV) cyavumbuwe mu 2019, cyaje kwitwa SARS-CoV-2, ni cyo cyateye icyorezo cy'indwara ya Coronavirus 2019 (COVID-19), cyahitanye abantu barenga 3 120 kugeza ku itariki ya 3 Werurwe 2020, naho umubare w'abanduye urenga 91 000.
Hari ikimenyetso cy'impungenge cyatanzwe, kandi isi igomba kwitegura icyorezo cya SARS-CoV-2.
Koronavirusi zirindwi zose z'abantu zaturutse mu nyamaswa, zituruka ku mpyisi, ku mpyisi cyangwa ku nyamaswa zo mu rugo.
Ibipimo byinshi by'amakuru bigaragaza ko koronavirus zose z'abantu zaturutse ku tugurube, utwo tugurube tugiye twigereranya neza kandi tudakoresha ibimenyetso byangiza indwara, ariko tugaragaza ubwirinzi bw'ibinyabuzima.
Icyorezo cya COVID-19 cyateye u Bushinwa n'isi yose ikibazo gikomeye mu by'ubuvuzi, mu bya siyansi, mu by'imibereho n'imico.
Kwiga ku buryo coronavirus zituruka mu nyamaswa bizatuma tumenya amateka yayo, imbaraga zituma ihinduka n'ibikumira ko abantu batandukana n'amoko.
