Abarwayi bake gusa bafite ubushobozi bwo kwirinda indwara, ni bo bonyine bagaragaje ko bafite indwara ikomeye yo mu buryo bw'ubuhumekero bwo hasi.
Icyorezo cya SARS, nanone cyitwa "epidémie de pneumonie atypique", ni cyo cya mbere mu mateka y'abantu cyanditswe neza cyatewe n'icyorezo cya coronavirus cyatewe n'abantu, kandi icyateye iki cyorezo ni virusi ya SARS-CoV, icyorezo cya gatatu cyatewe na coronavirus y'abantu.
Icyorezo cya SARS cyagaragaye bwa mbere mu mpera z'umwaka wa 2002 mu ntara ya Guangdong mu Bushinwa.
Mu gihe cy'icyorezo cya SARS, abantu 8,096 barwaye indwara n'abantu 774 barapfa, kandi indwara yageze mu bihugu byinshi no ku migabane itandukanye.
Uretse abanduza bakomeye, byateganyijwe ko buri muntu urwaye ashobora kwandura abandi bantu bagera kuri babiri; igihe cyo kurwara cy'iminsi 4 kugeza kuri 7, naho icyorezo cy'indwara cyageraga ku munsi wa 10 w'uburwayi.
Mu barwayi banduye SARS-CoV, mu ntangiriro habayeho ububabare bw'uruhu, umutwe, ubushyuhe, uburwayi rusange n'ibisebe, mu gihe mu bimenyetso bya nyuma harimo guhumeka, gusuka no guhumeka nabi.
Ibimenyetso by'ibisanzwe byerekana ko ibipimo by'ubuvuzi bya SARS bitandukanye n'ibisanzwe ni lymphophonie, ibibazo by'ibihaha n'ibipimo by'indwara ya creatine kinase.
Nanone abarwayi barwaye SARS bagaragaza ko bafite ubwonko buva mu nda, ko bakura ingirabuzimafatizo zo mu mubiri, kandi ko bafite ibipimo by'ibihaha by'umubiri.
Hafi 2030% by'abarwayi nyuma yaho bakeneye ubuvuzi bukomeye no guhumeka ibihaha.
Mu bihe bikomeye nk'ibyo, uretse imiyoboro yo hasi y'ubuhumekero, ibindi bice by'umubiri bishobora kwandura, harimo n'iby'urusoro, impyiko n'impyiko, akenshi bigaterwa n'umuyaga w'ibitoki ushobora guhitana, cyane cyane abarwayi bafite ubushobozi bwo kurwanya indwara.
