Iyi virusi yaturutse mu Buholandi, ariko mu by'ukuri ikwirakwira hose.
HCoV-NL63 igaragaza ko ari yo ituma abantu bagera kuri 4,7% barwara indwara zo mu myanya y'ubuhumekero, kandi ko indwara zitera zikaba ari nyinshi cyane mu mpeshyi, mu mpeshyi no mu itumba.
HCoV-NL63 ifitanye isano n'urwungano rw'ibinyabuzima (Larginite Obstructive), nanone bita urw'ibinyabuzima (Croup).
HCoV-HKU1 yagaragaye muri Hong Kong muri uwo mwaka, ku mugabo w'imyaka 71 wari warigeze kujya mu bitaro afite indwara ya pneumonie na bronchiolitis.
Uretse indwara zo mu mutwe zituruka mu bitaro n'iz'ubwonko, HCoV-HKU1 ifitanye isano n'indwara z'ubuhumekero.
Kimwe na HCoV-NL63, HCoV-229E na HCoV-OC43, virusi ya HCoV-HKU1, ituma abantu barwara indwara z'ubuhumekero z'ubwoko bworoheje, yasanze hirya no hino ku isi.
Izo koronavirusi enye z'abantu zitera ubwandu buturuka hanze y'ibitaro, zagiye zishyirwa mu bantu neza, kandi guhinduka kwazo zitera indwara ziterwa n'ubwandu busanzwe, birashoboka ko bitagenze neza, nubwo ibyabaye kandi impamvu zabyo zitazwi, nk'uko bigaragara mu rugero rudasanzwe rw'indwara y'ubwandu bw'indwara ya HCoV-NL63, ivugwaho ko yateje ubwandu bukomeye bw'imiyoboro yo hasi yo mu kirere mu Bushinwa.
Ubusanzwe iyo umuntu amaze kubona ubushobozi bwo gutwara no gukomeza kubaho neza, iyo virusi ya corona iba itakiri ingenzi cyangwa ngo ibe igendana n'ubwandu.
