Abenshi mu bantu bagaragaye ko banduye mu buryo bw'ibikorwaremezo bya laboratwari babayeho mu Burasirazuba bwo Hagati, ariko mu bihugu bitandukanye by'i Burayi no muri Tuniziya, habayeho ubwandu bwinjijwe no gukwirakwira hakoreshejwe ubwandu bw'indwara z'ibanze.
Hari ikindi cyorezo cya kabiri cy'abantu 186 cyamaze kwemezwa muri Koreya y'Epfo mu 2015.
Ibimenyetso bya kliniki by'indwara yo guhumeka yo mu Burasirazuba bwo Hagati (MERS) ni kimwe n'ibimenyetso by'indwara yo guhumeka ikomeye (SARS)  ku ndwara zombi biranga ubumuga bw'ikirere bw'ikirere.
Mu buryo butandukanye na SARS, abarwayi benshi bafite MERS na bo bagize ikibazo cy'impyiko, kikaba ari cyo kintu cyatandukanya MERS n'izindi ndwara ziterwa na koronavirusi zandurira ku bantu.
Abasaga 30% by'abarwayi bafite ibimenyetso by'amaraso, urugero nk'ihindagurika n'ibisindisha.
Ku itariki ya 14 Gashyantare 2020, hamaze kwandikwa abanduye barenga 2500 b'indwara yo guhumeka yo mu Burasirazuba bwo Hagati, bafite umubare munini w'abantu bapfa (34.4%), bityo MERS-CoV ifatwa nk'imwe mu virusi zihitana abantu cyane.
Mu mezi yo hagati na mu mpera z'ukwezi kwa cumi na kabiri mu mwaka wa 2019, mu mujyi wa Wuhan mu ntara ya Hubei mu Bushinwa, hamaze kuvumburwa amakipe y'abarwayi ba pneumonia ubu iyo ushubije amaso inyuma, bagaragaza ko ari indwara yatewe na coronavirus yo mu bwoko bwa 2 (SARS-CoV-2).
Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima ryatangaje ko icyorezo cy'indwara yo mu nzira zo mu myanya y'ubuhumekero ikomeje gutera, cyatewe na SARS-CoV-2, ari ikibazo cy'ubukene ku isi hose mu rwego rw'ubuzima bw'abaturage, kandi ko iki cyorezo cyiswe "indwara ya coronavirus 19" (COVID-19).
Kugeza ku itariki ya 3 Werurwe 2020, ku isi hemejwe ko habayeho abantu 90 053, naho ubwandu bukaba ari 3,4%.
Biragaragara ko mu ntara ya Hubei mu Bushinwa, umubare w'abapfa ari 4,2%, naho hanze yaho ni 1,2%.
SARS-CoV-2, kimwe na coronavirus ya SARS na MERS, ituma umuntu agira indwara ikomeye yo mu myanya y'ubuhumekero, igaragaza ubushyuhe, guhinda umushyitsi no guhumeka.
