Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku buzima ryatangaje ko COVID-19 ari icyorezo
Ku wa Gatatu, Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima (OMS) ryatangaje ko icyorezo cya COVID-19 cyandura cyatewe na coronavirus ya SARS-CoV-2.
Nubwo ijambo "icyorezo" ryerekeza ku rugero rw'indwara gusa, aho kwerekeza ku kaga k'ibyago by'ibyago, OMS ivuga ko leta z'ibihugu zigomba gufata ingamba:
Ibihugu byose hamwe biracyafite ubushobozi bwo kugira ingaruka ku iterambere ry'icyorezo.
Ibi bishoboka mu gihe ibihugu bizaba byita ku guhitamo, gupima, kuvura, kwiherera abarwayi, gukurikirana uburwayi, ndetse no guhamagarira abaturage babo, Umuyobozi Mukuru w'umuryango w'abibumbye w'abibumbye Tedros Adán Gebreísus yasobanuye.
Turi mu kaga cyane ku rugero rubabaje rw'ubwandu n'uburemere bw'iki cyorezo, ndetse no ku rugero rubabaje rw'ubudahangarwa
Dr. Tom Friedin wahoze ari umuyobozi w'Ikigo cya Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika Gishinzwe Kurinda no Gukumira Indwara, yavuze ko iki cyorezo kitigeze kibaho.
Mu kiganiro yagiranye na CNN mu kwezi kwa Gashyantare yavuze ko nta wundi virusi y'ubuhumekero uretse grippe yigeze ikurikiranwa kuva yatangira kugeza ku gukwirakwira ku isi hose.
Bwana Gebreissus yavuze igitekerezo nk'icyo, avuga ko tutari bwigere tubona icyorezo cyatewe na coronavirus.
Nanone kandi, ntitwigeze tubona icyorezo cy'indwara dushobora kugenzura.
Mu kwezi kwa mbere, OMS yatangaje ko iki cyorezo ari icyihebe cy'ubuzima rusange gifite akamaro mpuzamahanga, nyuma yaho ikacyita icyorezo.
Umuyobozi w'Ikigo cy'Igihugu cy'Imitsi n'indwara zandura muri Amerika, Dr. Anthony Fauci, yavuze ko iki cyorezo ari intangiriro gusa, ko kizakomeza kuba kibi kurushaho.
Amakuru dukesha Associated Press avuga ko ku wa kane ku isi habayeho nibura abantu 126,000 banduye COVID-19, abantu barenga 4.600 bakaba barapfuye.
Icyorezo cya Coronavirus 20192020  ni icyorezo cy'indwara ya coronavirus 2019 (COVID-19), cyatewe na coronavirus y'indwara yo guhumeka y'imbaraga ndende-2 (SARS-CoV-2).
Iki cyorezo cyagaragaye mu mujyi wa Wuhan mu Bushinwa mu Ukuboza 2019, ku itariki ya 30 Mutarama 2020 hatangajwe imimerere y'ibanze ku rwego mpuzamahanga mu bijyanye n'ubuzima bw'abaturage, nyuma yaho ku itariki ya 11 Werurwe 2020 hafatwa nk'icyorezo.
Ku itariki ya 10 Mata 2020, mu bihugu 210 no mu turere, abantu bagera kuri miliyoni 1.61 banduye COVID-19, bituma abantu bagera ku 97,000 bapfa.
Abantu bagera ku 364.000 barakize.
Mu Bushinwa, umubare w'abapfa ni 4%, mu gihe ku isi hose, uri hagati ya 13,04% muri Aljeriya na 0,08% muri Nouvelle-Zélande.
Ibimenyetso bikunze kugaragara cyane ni umuriro, gusonza no guhumeka nabi.
Hari izindi ndwara zishobora gutuma umuntu agira ibibazo, urugero nk'ubuhumekero bw'amaraso n'indwara y'ihumeka.
Igihe kuva ibimenyetso byatangira kugaragara kugeza igihe indwara irembeje, ubusanzwe kiba iminsi igera kuri itanu, ariko gishobora no kuva ku minsi ibiri kugeza ku minsi cumi n'ine.
Kugeza ubu nta rukingo cyangwa uburyo bwihariye bwo kuvura bwabonetse.
Uburyo bw'ingenzi bwo kuvura ni ubwonko bw'ibimenyetso n'ubw'ubufasha. Ingamba zo kwirinda zigusaba gukaraba intoki, guhisha umunwa mu gihe ufite ubumuga, kugumana abantu, kumenya no kwirinda abantu bakeka ko banduye.
Abayobozi ku isi yose bitabiriye icyo kibazo bashyizeho amategeko agenga ingendo, ingamba zo kwirinda, amasaha y'ikirenga, kugenzura ibyago mu kazi no gufunga ibigo bitandukanye.
Icyorezo cyateje ingaruka zikomeye ku bukungu n'imibereho y'abantu ku isi, kwimura cyangwa guhagarika ibikorwa bya siporo, iby'idini, ibya politiki n'iby'umuco, ndetse n'ubukene bw'ibicuruzwa bwakwirakwijwe n'ibintu by'agahinda.
Amashuri na kaminuza byafunzwe ku rwego rw'igihugu cyangwa akarere mu bihugu 193, bigira ingaruka ku banyeshuri bagera kuri 99.4% ku isi.
Hari amakuru atari yo kuri iyi virusi yatangiye gukwirakwira kuri interineti, habayeho ikibazo cy'ubutagondwa no kurenganywa ku baturage b'u Bushinwa, abandi baturage bo mu Burasirazuba no mu Majyepfo y'Iburasirazuba bwa Aziya, cyangwa abantu babagereranya n'abandi baturage, ndetse no ku bandi bantu baba mu turere tuzwiho ko hari umubare munini w'abantu banduye iyi virusi.
Kubera ko umubare w'abantu bajyayo wagabanutse, n'ibigo by'inganda zikomeye byarahagaritswe, umwuka wahumanyijwe n'umwuka wa karuboni wagabanutse.
Ku itariki ya 31 Ukuboza 2019, inzego z'ubuzima mu mujyi wa Wuhan (umurwa mukuru w'intara ya Hubei, mu Bushinwa) zatangaje ko hari abantu banduye indwara ya Pneumonia ku mpamvu zitazwi, mu ntangiriro za Mutarama 2020 hatangiye iperereza ku kibazo.
Ibihe by'ubwandu ahanini byahuye n'isoko ry'ibikomoka ku nyanja rya Huang, bityo virusi bivugwa ko ifite inkomoko mu karere k'amafi.
Iyi virusi yatumye iyi ndwara itangira, izwi nka SARS-CoV-2. Ni virusi iherutse kuvumburwa ifite isano cyane na coronavirus y'ingurube, coronavirus ya pangolin na SARS-CoV. Nyuma byamenyekanye ko icyorezo cya mbere cy'iyi ndwara cyabaye ku itariki ya 1 Ukuboza 2019, kandi umuntu wanduye ntiyigeze agera ku isoko nyuma y'uwo munsi.
Ibice bibiri bya gatatu by'abanduye mu kwezi k'Ukuboza 2019 byari bifitanye isano n'iki isoko.
Ku itariki ya 13 Werurwe 2020, mu kinyamakuru cyo mu Bushinwa cyo mu Majyepfo cyitwa Morning Post, amakuru yayo ntiyashyizwe ahagaragara, hatanzwe igitekerezo cy'uko umuntu wa mbere w'imyaka 55 wanduye indwara ya Hubei ku itariki ya 17 Ugushyingo 2019. Ku itariki ya 26 Gashyantare 2020, OMS yatangaje ko umubare w'abanduye indwara nshya mu Bushinwa wagabanutse ariko ugenda wiyongera mu buryo butunguranye mu Butaliyani, Irani na Koreya y'Epfo, kandi ko umubare w'abanduye indwara nshya hanze y'u Bushinwa urenze umubare w'abanduye indwara nshya mu Bushinwa ku ncuro ya mbere.
Umubare w'abandura indwara ushobora kugabanuka cyane, cyane cyane kubera ko hari abantu benshi bafite ibimenyetso byoroheje.
Ku itariki ya 26 Gashyantare, habayeho ubwandu buke cyane mu rubyiruko, mu gihe abarwayi bafite imyaka 19 n'abatarengeje imyaka 19 aribo bari hasi ya 2,4% ku isi yose. Patrick Wallans, umujyanama mukuru mu by'ubumenyi mu Bwongereza, yavuze ko 60% by'abaturage b'u Bwongereza bazaba banduye kugeza igihe abaturage bazatangira kugira ubwirinzi bw'itsinda.
Muri iyo mibare harimo abantu bageragejwe COVID-19 kandi bageragejwe ko bafite ibimenyetso byemeza ko banduye.
Kugeza ku itariki ya 23 Werurwe nta gihugu na kimwe cyabashije gupima abaturage bacyo barenga 3% kandi mu bihugu byinshi nka Italiya, Ubuholandi, Esipanye na Suisse, hakozwe politiki yemewe yo kudakora ibizamini mu gihe hari ibimenyetso byoroheje gusa.
Ubushakashatsi bwashyizwe ahagaragara ku wa 16 Werurwe, bwagaragaje ko mu Bushinwa kugeza ku wa 23 Mutarama, 86% by'abanduye COVID-19 ntibari barabonetse, kandi ko abarwayi batanditswe nk'abo ari bo babaye isoko y'indwara kuri 79% by'abanduye.
Isesengura ry'imibare ryasohowe ku itariki ya 30 Werurwe ryagaragaje ko umubare w'abanduye mu by'ukuri mu Butaliyani warenze cyane umubare w'abanduye.
Ibipimo by'ibanze by'umubare w'ubwandu bw'ubwandu (R0) kuri COVID-19 byari hagati ya 1,4 na 2,4.
