Gukaraba intoki buri gihe n'isabune mu bihe bimwe na bimwe by'ingenzi mu munsi bifasha kwirinda indwara nyinshi, urugero nk'ibicurane n'ihindagurika, byanduzwa n'inshyi.
Umuntu ashobora no kwandura indwara z'ubuhumekero, urugero nk'ibicurane cyangwa icyorezo cy'ibicurane, urugero nko gukorakora ku maso, mu mazuru cyangwa mu kanwa (ni ukuvuga mu gice cy'urwondo rw'amaraso) n'amaboko adahise.
Hari ibintu bitanu by'ingenzi mu munsi ugomba gukaraba intoki ukoresheje isabune: mbere na nyuma yo gutakaza isuku, nyuma yo gukaraba amagufa cyangwa guhindurira imyenda, mbere yo kugaburira umwana, mbere yo kurya, mbere na nyuma yo gutegura cyangwa gutunganya inyama zitari nke, amafi n'ibiguruka.
Niba amazi n'isabune bidahari, ushobora gukora isuku ukoresheje igishura. Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima (OMS) ritera inkunga abantu ko bakaraba intoki:
Mbere, mu gihe no nyuma yo guteka.
Mbere na nyuma yo kwita ku murwayi.
Nyuma yo guhindura imyenda cyangwa gukaraba umwana wari wagiye mu bwiherero.
Nyuma yo kurira, guhinda cyangwa gusinzira.
Nyuma yo gukora ku nyamaswa, ibiryo cyangwa imyanda y'inyamaswa.
Ubudahumana bw'amaboko buvuga ibikorwa by'isuku bifitanye isano n'imikorere y'ubuvuzi.
Gukaraba intoki mbere yo gufata imiti cyangwa uburyo bwo kwivuza bizatuma indwara zitandura cyangwa zigakwirakwira.
Intego y'ibanze y'ubuvuzi yo gukaraba intoki ni ugukura intoki ku bintu byangiza umubiri (bakiteri, virusi cyangwa ibindi bintu bishobora gutera indwara), ndetse no ku bintu by'ubumara bishobora guteza indwara runaka.
Iyi gahunda ni ingenzi cyane ku bantu bakora ibiryo cyangwa bakora mu buvuzi, ariko ni ingenzi no ku bandi bantu bose.
Gukaraba intoki ni ingirakamaro cyane ku buzima: urugero, bigabanya icyorezo cya Grippe, Coronavirus n'izindi ndwara zandura, bigabanya indwara zandura z'urwungano, bigabanya ubwandu bw'indwara zo mu myanya y'ubuhumekero,
kandi igabanya umubare w'abana bapfa babyaye mu rugo.
Ubushakashatsi bwakozwe mu mwaka wa 2013 bwagaragaje ko gukaraba intoki mu buryo bwiza bishobora gutuma abana bari munsi y'imyaka itanu batinda kwiyongera.
Mu bihugu biri mu nzira y'amajyambere, umubare w'abana bapfa bazize indwara zo mu myanya y'ubuhumekero n'iz'ubuhumekero ushobora kugabanuka binyuze mu gukora ibintu byoroheje, urugero nko gukaraba intoki n'isabune.
Iyo gahunda yoroheje ishobora kugabanya urupfu rw'abantu bahitanwa n'iyo ndwara hafi ku kigero cya 50%.
Kwibuka akamaro ko gukaraba intoki buri gihe bishobora kugabanya umubare w'abandura indwara y'ibicurane ku kigero cya gatatu, kandi ibyo bigereranywa n'inyungu zo kubona amazi meza mu turere tudafite amikoro make.
Kugabanya umubare w'abandura indwara z'uruhu ku kigero cya 48% bishobora guterwa no gukaraba intoki n'isabune. Gukaraba intoki n'isabune  ni uburyo bumwe rukumbi kandi bworoshye bwo kwirinda uruhu n'indwara zihitana mu guhumeka (ORD) mu gihe umuntu yakora imyitozo ikwiye mu rugo, mu mashuri no mu bindi bice by'abaturage hirya no hino ku isi.
Pneumonie, kimwe mu byorezo by'indwara y'ubwonko bw'ibinyabuzima, ni cyo gitera abana batarageza ku myaka itanu gupfa, kandi gihitana abana bagera kuri miliyoni 1.8 buri mwaka.
Buri mwaka, abana bagera hafi kuri miriyoni 3.5 bahitanwa n'indwara y'ibicurane n'imyotsi.
Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku bana rivuga ko gukaraba intoki n'isabune mbere yo kurya no nyuma yo kujya mu bwiherero, ari ibintu bisanzwe, bishobora gukiza abantu benshi kurusha urukingo cyangwa ubuvuzi ubwo ari bwo bwose, kandi bikagabanya urupfu rw'abafite iseseme hafi kuri kabiri, n'urupfu rw'abafite indwara z'ubuhumekero bw'ubuhumekero bukabije ku kigero cya kane.
Gukaraba intoki ubusanzwe bihuza n'ibindi bikorwa by'isuku bikorwa mu rwego rw'ibikorwa by'amazi, isuku n'isuku (WASH).
Gukaraba intoki na byo bifasha kwirinda indwara yo kutagira ubushobozi bwo kwanduza umuntu, iyo umuntu ahuriye na yo mu buryo bw'umubiri.
Kugira ngo umuntu akomeze gukaraba intoki kenshi, bishobora gutuma akomeza kumera nabi.
Ubushakashatsi bwo mu gihugu cya Danimarike bwo mu mwaka wa 2012 bwagaragaje ko gukaraba intoki kenshi bishobora gutuma umuntu agira ubukana n'ubushishi mu ruhu, bigatuma arwara indwara izwi ku izina rya ekzeme cyangwa dermatite y'intoki, cyane cyane mu baganga mu by'ubuvuzi.
Gukaraba intoki kenshi cyane na byo bishobora kuba kimwe mu bimenyetso by'indwara yo kwiheba no kudakora ibintu mu buryo bwa bwite (OCD).
Hari ibihe bitanu by'ingenzi mu munsi aho gukaraba intoki n'isabune ari ngombwa kugira ngo umuntu akomeze kugabanya ibyago byo kwandura indwara: nyuma yo gusuka (kugwa, gusuka), nyuma yo gukaraba intoki z'umwana (guhindura imyenda), mbere yo kurya, mbere yo kurya no mbere/nyuma yo gutegura cyangwa gutunganya inyama zitari ziko, amafi cyangwa inyoni.
Hari n'ibindi bihe umuntu agomba gukaraba intoki kugira ngo atabyandura: mbere cyangwa nyuma yo gukemura igihombo cyangwa igikomere, nyuma yo guturika, guhosha cyangwa gukubita, nyuma yo gukora ku bintu by'amatungo cyangwa ku nyamaswa, nyuma yo gukora ku ruswa.
Mu bihugu byinshi, gukaraba intoki n'isabune si ibintu bisanzwe.
Ubushakashatsi bwakozwe mu 2015 ku myitozo y'intoki mu bihugu 54 bwagaragaje ko ku kigereranyo, mu miryango 38,7% yo mu isi, gukaraba intoki n'isabune ari umuco w'abantu benshi. Ubushakashatsi bwo mu mwaka wa 2014 bwagaragaje ko umubare munini cyane, 97%, wabonywe muri Arabiya Sawudite; Amerika iri hafi y'icya kabiri muri urwo rutonde, umubare wabo uri 77%; igipimo cyo hasi cyane cyanditswe mu Bushinwa ni 23%.
