Mu mpera z'imyaka ya 1990 no mu ntangiriro z'ikinyejana cya 21, ibikoresho byo guhumeka intoki ku buryo bufite inzoga, bitagira amazi (bikanamenyekana nk'ibikoresho byo guhumeka intoki ku buryo bufite inzoga, imiti yo guhumeka intoki cyangwa sanitaziseri) byatangiye gukundwa cyane.
Ibi bikoresho byinshi byakozwe hakoreshejwe izopropyl alcohol cyangwa ethanol, byongewemo ibihuha nka carbomere (polymer ya acrylic acid) mu buryo bwa gel, cyangwa ibihuha nka glycerine mu buryo bw'amazi cyangwa mu buryo bw'umusemburo, bituma bikoreshwa neza kandi bikongeraho ingaruka zo gukaraba uruhu n'inzoga.
Iyo umuntu yongeyeho hydrogen peroxide, bituma ikinyabuzima kirushaho gukora neza.
