Gucunga ibikorwa by'ikoranabuhanga mu bijyanye na COVID-19
Kugenzura ibikorwa by'ikoranabuhanga bijyanye na COVID-19 bisobanura gukoresha uburyo bwo kugenzura umutekano w'akazi no kurinda ubuzima mu rwego rwo kugenzura ibyago no kurwanya icyorezo cya Coronavirus cyo mu mwaka wa 2019 (COVID-19).
Kugenzura ibyago mu kazi bikwiye bitewe n'aho ukorera n'akazi ukora, bishingiye ku gupima ibyago, uburemere bw'icyorezo mu baturage, n'ibyago ku bakozi bamwe na bamwe bashobora kuba bafite ubukana kubera COVID-19.
Ikigo cya Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika gishinzwe umutekano mu kazi n'isuku mu by'inganda (OSHA) cyatangaje ko imirimo ifite ibyago bike cyane ifite imishyikirano ya bugufi n'abaturage n'abo bakorana, kandi ko ibyo bisaba ingamba z'ibanze zo kurwanya indwara, zirimo gukaraba intoki, gushishikariza abakozi kuguma mu rugo mu gihe hari ibimenyetso by'indwara, kubahiriza amabwiriza yo guhumeka, no gukora isuku no guhumanura indwara buri munsi.
Imyanya ifite ibyago bigera hagati igusaba guhura kenshi cyangwa hafi n'abantu badafite icyorezo cya COVID-19 cyemejwe cyangwa bakekwaho, ariko bashobora kwandura kubera ko iki cyorezo gikomeje gukwirakwira mu baturage cyangwa mu ngendo mpuzamahanga.
Aba bantu bashobora kuba ari abakozi bagirana na rubanda, urugero nk'amashuri, ahantu ho gukorera abantu benshi ndetse no mu maduka manini amwe n'amwe.
Ibikorwa byo kugenzura ibyago by'iyi kipe, uretse ingamba z'ibanze zo kwirinda indwara, birimo guhumeka hakoreshejwe ibicungajuru bifite ingufu nyinshi, gukoresha udukingirizo n'ibikoresho by'ubwirinzi ku giti cyawe mu gihe uhuye n'umuntu urwaye COVID-19.
OSHA ivuga ko abakozi bo mu bigo by'ubuvuzi n'iby'amaraso bagiranye na muntu ufite icyorezo cya COVID-19 cyemejwe cyangwa ukekwaho ko afite icyorezo cya COVID-19 ari bo bafite ibyago byinshi; aho usanga ibyago byiyongera cyane iyo abo bakozi bakora ibikorwa byo gukora icyorezo cya COVID-19, cyangwa gutora/gukora ibizamini ku muntu ufite icyorezo cya COVID-19 cyemejwe cyangwa ukekwaho ko afite icyorezo cya COVID-19.
Ingamba zo kugenzura ibyago zikwiriye abakozi nk'abo zirimo gukoresha ibikoresho by'ubuhanga n'umutekano, urugero nk'ibyumba bifite umwuka mubi, hamwe n'ibikoresho by'ubwirinzi bihuje n'icyo gikorwa.
Icyorezo cya COVID-19 gishobora kugira ingaruka zitandukanye mu kazi.
Abakozi bashobora kuba batari ku kazi kubera uburwayi bwabo, kwita ku bandi cyangwa kubera ubwoba bwo kwandura.
Uburyo bwo kugura ibicuruzwa n'uburyo bwo kugura ibicuruzwa (urugero, kugura mu bihe bitagoranye no gutanga cyangwa gukora imirimo itari mu modoka) bishobora guhinduka.
Amaherezo, hari igihe ibintu bishobora gutandukana n'ibicuruzwa biva mu turere two mu karere ka COVID-19.
Izo gahunda zisaba ibibazo by'ibyago bijyanye n'akazi n'akazi, harimo inkomoko y'ubwandu, ibyago byibasira mu rugo no mu baturage, ndetse n'ibyago byibasira abakozi bamwe na bamwe, urugero nk'iza bukuru cyangwa indwara zidakira.
Izo gahunda zigaragaza kandi uburyo bwo kugenzura ibyo bibazo bikenewe kugira ngo ibibazo by'ibyo byago bikemuke, ndetse n'ingamba z'ubutabazi ku bibazo bishobora guterwa n'icyorezo.
