Imwe mu ntego zo gutanga ingamba zo guhangana n'icyorezo ni ukugabanya ikwirakwira rya virusi mu bakozi, kurinda abantu bafite ibyago byinshi byo kugira ibibazo bikomeye by'ubuzima, gukomeza ibikorwa by'ubucuruzi no kugabanya ingaruka mbi ku zindi nzego mu mitororokano yazo.
Ibisubizo by'ibyo bibazo bigerwaho n'uko indwara ziteye mu gace umuntu akoreramo ubucuruzi.
Urwego rw'ibikoresho byo kugenzura ibyago  ni urwego rukoreshwa cyane mu guharanira umutekano n'isuku ku kazi, mu gushyira ibyo bikoresho mu matsinda bitewe n'uko bikora neza.
Iyo nta kintu na kimwe gishobora gukemura ibyago byo kurwara COVID-19, ibikoresho by'ubuhanga n'umutekano ni byo bifite akamaro cyane, nyuma y'ibyo ni ibijyanye n'ubuyobozi, hanyuma ni ibijyanye n'ubwirinzi.
Ingufu z'ubugenzuzi zigamije kwirinda abakozi mu gihe bakora akazi, kandi ntizikurikize imyitwarire y'umukozi, kuko bishobora kuba ari byo bifasha cyane.
Ingamba z'ubuyobozi zigaragaza ko hari ibyo umuntu agomba guhindura mu mikorere y'akazi cyangwa mu mikorere y'akazi.
Ibikoresho by'ubwirinzi (PPE) bifatwa ko bidafite akamaro ugereranyije n'ingamba z'ubuhanga cyangwa z'ubuyobozi, ariko bishobora gufasha mu gukemura ibyago bimwe na bimwe.
