Ariko uretse kwirinda ibintu byinshi, twabonye itsinda ry'abakora isuku yo guhanagura virusi kugira ngo ryangirize ahantu hose mu biro byacu byo mu mujyi wa San Francisco.
Bakoresheje imiti y'ubuvuzi ikoreshwa mu kurwanya virusi kugira ngo bashobore guhumanya imiterere yose y'ubutaka, ndetse no mu byumba by'abitabiriye no mu byumba by'amaherero by'amazu y'amazu y'amazu y'amazu y'amazu y'amazu y'amazu y'amazu, aho bashoboraga kwinjira mu nzu yacu.
Inzu ikoresha amategeko yayo bwite agusaba kwitonda, ukoresheje ibicuruzwa byemeza umutekano w'abacyubakira.
Twumva ko ibiro byacu bizateguzwa neza igihe tuzaba dufata umwanzuro wo gusubira mu rugo.
Ibiro byacu byo muri leta ya Columbia (DC) biri ku rubuga rwa WeWork, rwatubwiye amategeko yayo ku bijyanye na COVID-19 hamwe n'abakozi bose bo muri DC.
Mu cyumweru gishize, ibiro byacu byo mu Karere ka Columbia byagiye byimukira kure mu buryo bwuzuye nk'uko ubuyobozi bwa San Francisco bwabitegetse.
Nk'uko bamwe mu bakozi bacu bo mu mujyi wa New York babizi, twaganiriye kandi ku kibazo cyo gukodesha inzu i Brooklyn.
Ibiganiro nk'ibyo birakomeza, ariko bishobora gutangwa.
Bamwe mu bakozi bacu ni ubwa mbere bakora akazi kure.
Abo twakoranaga kera bakora kure, bazi ko ushobora guhindura ibintu, kandi bagashaka kuguha inama:
Ni byiza ko inama ziba amasaha abiri cyangwa arenga.
Niba ukeneye gukora amasaha menshi, jya utekereza ku buryo ushobora kuyahindura indi minsi.
Shyiraho intego y'inama, gahunda y'umunsi w'inama kandi ujye ubanza utange ibikubiyemo.
Koresha videwo nk'ibisanzwe, koresha ibikoresho nka Google Docs na Zoom kugira ngo byorohereze ibiganiro no kuvugana.
Kugira ngo ubikorere neza, shyiraho umuntu uhuza ibiganiro, uzajya akurikirana ibibazo by'abantu bavugana, kandi uzajya ugenzura urutonde rw'abavuga, kandi uzajya ugenzura ibyo uvuze (cyangwa uzajya ugenzura hamwe).
Niba ukeneye gukoresha umudari mwiza, uzajye wandika kuri serivisi y'ubufasha bwa tekiniki kuri interineti.
Koresha inyungu zawe zo muri gahunda ya Wellness Reimbursement mu gihe ugura ibyokurya by'agateganyo.
Jya kuri Slack ukoresheje ikoranabuhanga rya #remoties kugira ngo uganire n'abo mukorana ku kazi gafite aho gaherereye.
Itsinda rya HR Operations ririmo kwiga amabwiriza y'ikoranabuhanga, aboneka mu buryo bwa webinar kugira ngo ibikorwa by'ishyirahamwe ryose bikorwe neza.
Mu cyumweru gishize, twasabye abahawe inkunga y'umuryango bose guhagarika ibikorwa by'ubwoko bwose bishyigikirwa na Wikimedia, urugero nka editathons, kugeza ubwo OMS izaba yatangaje ko icyorezo kirangiye.
Tuzi kandi turavuga ko ibyo dusaba kugabanya ibyo bikorwa n'ibindi bihano bishobora gutuma tudashobora gukora ibikorwa by'inyungu byemejwe, kandi nta muntu n'umwe uzajya ahanwa amafaranga yo kubishyira mu bikorwa cyangwa guhindura intego.
Mu cyumweru gitaha tuzakora ibikorwa bikurikiraho, tuzaba dufite ibindi bisobanuro kuri Wikimania, ndetse n'ibindi biganiro by'akarere n'iby'ingingo rusange.
Umwuka rusange mu muryango w'isi yose  ntabwo ari agahinda gusa ku mpamvu yo guhagarika akazi, ahubwo ni no kumva ko hari icyaruhutse ku mpamvu yo gusobanukirwa no kwibanda ku baturage bacu, Wikimedia ndetse n'ibindi.
Ku bijyanye n'imyumvire, CRT ikora ku ipaji ya Meta-Wiki izaha akarere k'abaturage aho bashobora gukurikirana ingaruka n'imishyikirano.
