Porogaramu za COVID-19 ni porogaramu za telefoni zigenewe gufasha mu iperereza ry'icyorezo mu gihe cy'icyorezo cya coronavirus cy'umwaka wa 2019-20, ni ukuvuga mu kumenya abantu (abafitanye isano) bashoboraga guhura n'umuntu wanduye.
Mu turere tumwe na tumwe, hari porogaramu nyinshi zashyizweho cyangwa zatanzwe, zishigikiwe n'ubutegetsi.
Hari uburyo bwinshi bwo gukurikirana abantu.
Ibi byateye impaka ku bibazo by'ibanga, cyane cyane ku birebana n'uburyo bushingiye ku gukurikirana aho abakoresha porogaramu bari.
Ibindi byoroheje muri ibyo birimo gukoresha ibimenyetso bya Bluetooth kugira ngo umuntu abone uko yegera izindi telefoni zigendanwa.
Ku itariki ya 10 Mata 2020, Google na Apple batangaje ko bagiye guhuza imbaraga zabo mu gushyiraho uburyo bwo gushyigikira izi porogaramu zishingiye kuri Bluetooth mu buryo butaziguye muri sisitemu zabo za Android na iOS.
Mu Bushinwa, leta ifatanyije na Alipay, yashyizeho porogaramu ituma abaturage bashobora kureba niba bavuganye n'abantu banduye COVID-19.
Ikoreshwa mu mijyi irenga 200 yo mu Bushinwa. Muri Singapore hari porogaramu yitwa TraceTogether.
Iyo porogaramu yashyizweho n'ibigo by'ikoranabuhanga byo mu karere, ifite code y'ibanze kandi izashyirwa ku buyobozi bwa guverinoma.
Iyi porogaramu yashyizweho na Minisiteri y'Ubuzima n'Ubuvugizi.
Ku itariki ya 14 Mata 2020, porogaramu yari itegereje kwiyandikisha muri Google Play Store na Apple App Store.
Ku itariki ya 12 Mata, guverinoma yatangaje ko porogaramu yo gukurikirana abagenzi iri mu cyiciro cya nyuma cyo gukora kandi ko izaboneka mu byumweru bike. Porogaramu nk'izo ziteganyijwe gutangira mu gihugu cya Ireland no mu Bufaransa (StopCovid).
Australia na New Zealand zirimo gusuzuma uburyo bwo gukoresha porogaramu ishingiye kuri porogaramu ya TraceTogether yo muri Singapore na protocole ya BlueTrace. Uburusiya bufite intego yo gukoresha porogaramu ifite akazi ko gucapa ahantu, igamije  gukurikirana ko abarwayi bafite icyorezo cya COVID-19, baba i Moscow batava mu ngo zabo.
Ross Anderson, umwarimu wigisha umutekano muri Kaminuza ya Cambridge, agaragaza ibibazo by'ikoranabuhanga bishobora kuvuka mu mikorere y'ibikoresho, harimo kubeshya no kubura icyo bikora mu gihe igice gito cy'abaturage ari cyo cyose cyikoresha.
Kubera impungenge ku bihereranye no gukwirakwiza porogaramu ziyobya cyangwa zifite ubukana bwa Coronavirus, Apple yagabanyije urutonde rw'ibigo bishobora gutanga porogaramu za Coronavirus muri App Store, ikagaragaza gusa porogaramu z'ibanze cyangwa izindi nzego ziringirwa.
Google na Amazon na byo byashyizeho amategeko nk'ayo.
Abari mu mushinga wo kurinda ubuzima bwite bagaragaje impungenge ku ngaruka zo kugenzura abaturage ku bwinshi binyuze mu porogaramu zifitanye isano na coronavirus; byongeyeho ko ikibazo cy'uko ibikorwa by'ubwubatsi byakozwe mu kurwanya icyorezo cya coronavirus bizasenyurwa igihe icyo cyorezo kizaba cyarangiye.
Umuryango mpuzamahanga wita ku bantu bababariwe ibyaha (Amnesty International) n'indi miryango isaga 100 basohoye itangazo risaba ko hakorwa ubugenzuzi.
