Mu bihugu bimwe na bimwe, aho gukoresha porogaramu, hakoreshwa uburyo bwo gukurikirana aho abantu bari, bityo ntihagire umuntu ugomba gupakira porogaramu cyangwa ngo agire icyo akora kugira ngo yirinde gukurikirana.
Muri Isirayeli, gukurikira abantu ku mbuga za interineti byemewe.
Ibisubizo byo kuri interineti bigira aho bigana amakuru y'aho biri nabyo bifite ibibazo bikomeye by'ibanga.
Ariko ntabwo gahunda zose zifite seriveri z'ibanze zigomba kugira amakuru bwite yerekeye aho zikorera; hari serivisi z'ibanga zakozwe zikoresha seriveri z'ibanze gusa kugirango zihurize (reba igice cyo hasi).
Muri Koreya y'Epfo, hakoreshejwe uburyo butakoresha porogaramu nk'urufatiro rwo gukurikirana abantu.
Aho gukoresha porogaramu yihariye, porogaramu yakusanyaga amakuru yo gukurikirana mu buryo butandukanye, harimo amakuru yo gukurikirana ibikoresho bya telefoni n'ibicuruzwa bya karita, hanyuma ikabishyira hamwe kugira ngo ibimenyeshejwe mu buryo bw'amajwi byoherezwa ku bantu bashobora kuba banduye.
Guverinoma ntiyakoresheje gusa ayo makuru mu kuburira abaturage ku bijyanye n'aho bashobora guhurira n'abantu banduye, ahubwo nanone yashyize amakuru y'aho baba ahagaragara, ibyo bikaba byaratumye bishoboka kubera impinduka zikomeye mu mategeko arengera amakuru zashyizweho nyuma y'aho MERS yadutse muri icyo gihugu.
Ibi bihugu birimo n'u Budage, birimo gutekereza ku buryo bwo gukoresha sisitemu zigenzura ibintu, ndetse n'uburyo bwo kubungabunga ibyangombwa by'ibanga.
