Nitasoxainide yagaragajwe mu bushakashatsi bwakozwe mu buzima bwa buri munsi, igaragaza ko ihinika SARS-CoV-2 mu biciro bike. Ubushakashatsi bwagaragaje ko kugira ngo SARS-CoV-2 yinjire binyuze mu guhuza na ACE2 receptor, bisaba ko igishyimbo cy'umusemburo cyitwa serine 2 (TMPRSS2) cyashyirwamo.
Ubushakashatsi ku ikoreshwa rya chlorine na hydroxychloroquine na azithromycin cyangwa idafite bifite imipaka ikomeye ituma umuryango w'ubuvuzi utemera gukoresha ubu buryo bw'ubuvuzi nta makuru menshi. Oseltimavir ntinaniza SARS-CoV-2 in vitro, kandi uruhare rwayo mu kuvura COVID-19 ntiruraboneka.
Hari igihe indwara ya hypercytoquinemia ishobora guterwa n'indwara ikomeye ya COVID-19 mu bihe by'iherezo.
Hari ibimenyetso bigaragaza ko hydroxychloroquine ishobora kugira ubushobozi bwo kurinda indwara ya hypercytoquine. Ubushakashatsi buto bwakozwe na Komisiyo y'Igihugu y'Ubuzima mu Bushinwa, bwagaragaje ko tocilizumab ari yo ihabwa abantu mu gihe bakoresha imiti yo kuvura coronavirus.
Iki kiyobyabwenge cyasohotse mu cyiciro cya 2 cy'igeragezwa ritamenyekanye, rikaba ribera mu gihugu cyose mu Butaliyani, nyuma y'uko habonetse ibisubizo byiza by'uko cyakoreshejwe mu barwayi bafite indwara ikomeye.
Iyo ikoranywe n'umusaruro w'amaraso w'umusaruro w'ibinyabuzima byitwa ferritine kugira ngo haboneke ibihuha by'ibikomoka ku bice by'umubiri, iba igamije kurwanya ibintu bivugwa ko bituma abantu bamwe bapfa.
Mu 2017, FDA yemeje ko interleukin-6 ari ikinyuranyo cy'ingenzi cy'ingenzi cy'ubushakashatsi bwakozwe nyuma y'igihe, mu kuvura indwara yo gutakaza sitokini zitera sitorayi zitera ubukana, ziterwa n'indi mpamvu, ari yo CAR.
Kugeza ubu nta bimenyetso byerekeranye kandi by'ubugenzuzi byabonetse bigaragaza ko tocilizumab ari umuti mwiza wo kuvura indwara yo gutakaza sitokini.
Gutanga imiti ihumura kandi igamije kurwanya indwara z'uburwayi z'abarwayi bakira COVID-19 ku bantu babikeneye, ubu bigereranywa n'uburyo bwo gukingira budafite urukingo.
Iyi ngamba yageragejwe mu kuvura abarwayi ba SARS, ariko ibisubizo byayo ntibyumvikana.
Kwifata mu nda bya virusi  ni ingaruka zategerejwe, aho imiti ikora ku mubiri ishobora gutuma wirinda SARS-CoV-2.
Ariko kandi, hari n'izindi ngamba zishobora gukoreshwa, urugero nk'ubwandu bw'ingirabuzimafatizo zidakora ku mubiri n'ubundi cyangwa fagositosi.
Ibindi bikorwa byo kuvura umubiri mu buryo budafite icyo bugamije, urugero nko gukoresha imiti ikoreshwa mu kuvura umubiri mu buryo bw'umubiri, biri gukorwa.
Hari uburyo bwo kongera ingano y'amaraso y'abakize bakoresheje umuti w'amaraso, ugizwe n'amaraso y'abakize kandi ufite imiti irwanya virusi.
